Date: Tue, 9 Jul 2024 09:24:38 +0300
Subject: [PATCH] Force cross-compile

We need to be able to trigger configure's cross code but we don't want
to set cross_prefix as it does other things we don't want. Patch things
so we can do what we need in the target config case.
---
 configure | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/configure b/configure
index 3cd736b139..dd35984b1c 100755
--- a/configure
+++ b/configure
@@ -174,7 +174,7 @@ fi
 # default parameters
 container_engine="auto"
 cpu=""
-cross_compile="no"
+cross_compile="yes"
 cross_prefix=""
 host_cc="cc"
 EXTRA_CFLAGS=""
